# generated brand assets — rendered by `.brand/build-brand.mjs` (the source of
# truth) from `.brand/fonts/`. Keep the generator + fonts, never the output.
# Regenerate with: node .brand/build-brand.mjs
.brand/*.png
.brand/*.svg
